assertTrue(true) is meaningless and confusing. By default, if you get to
point X of a test, then all must be well so far, otherwise the next line
will be &quot;fail(...)&quot;. Don&#39;t write assertTrue(true). :)

Let the framework communicate; it&#39;s a good one!

